raw_data.title: Senior Principal
raw_data.description: Functions as a company director and corporate monitor overseeing all aspects of the company. Authorized to commit the company contractually, procure subcontracts, and hire staff. Monitors financial and technical progress of projects, resolves problems, and directly participates in complex projects. Experience includes leading large contracts and/or complex project teams. Expert in the use of relevant analytical, methodological, and management tools needed to organize, perform and deliver all services being provided. Provides oversight and assures appropriate execution of all major project activities. Provides quality control and final review of all project deliverables.
